      "writtenOn": "2019-01-08T02:24:40Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Actually, actually, I think this still needs the reinterpret_cast\u003c\u003e()s in the calls to StringToNumber() since we want to choose specific overloads and in order to be safely reinterpretable, `data` needs to be a char array.",
